Combine @brown sugar{1.5%cup}, @ketchup{1.5%cup}, @red wine vinegar{1/2%cup}, @water{1/2%cup}, and @Worcestershire sauce{1%Tbsp} in a #blender{}.

Season with @mustard{2.5%Tbsp}, @paprika{2%tsp}, @salt{2%tsp}, @black pepper{1.5%tsp}, and @hot pepper sauce{2%dashes}. Blend until smooth. ~{10%minutes}
